<collectingRegion box="[511,657,223,248]" country="Papua New Guinea" name="New Ireland" pageId="216" pageNumber="217">New Ireland</collectingRegion>
: 1, 2.—General distribution: Red Sea, East Africa, 
<collectingCountry box="[1251,1386,223,248]" name="Madagascar" pageId="216" pageNumber="217">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
and western Mascarenes east to 
<collectingCountry box="[461,587,260,285]" name="Philippines" pageId="216" pageNumber="217">Philippines</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[640,735,261,284]" name="Vanuatu" pageId="216" pageNumber="217">Vanuatu</collectingCountry>
, north to Ryukyu Islands and southern 
<collectingCountry box="[1169,1236,261,284]" name="Japan" pageId="216" pageNumber="217">Japan</collectingCountry>
, south to northern 
<collectingCountry box="[151,257,295,320]" name="Australia" pageId="216" pageNumber="217">Australia</collectingCountry>
. Solitary on sheltered coastal reefs, in lagoons and on exposed offshore reefs, 
<quantity box="[1132,1217,296,320]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.5" metricValueMax="12.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="216" pageNumber="217" unit="m" value="6.5" valueMax="12.0" valueMin="1.0">1–12 m</quantity>
